  "page": "Aemon Targaryen",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Aemon Targaryen</b> is the name of several members of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\">House Targaryen</a>. These include:\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Aemon_Targaryen_(son_of_Jaehaerys_I)\" title=\"Aemon Targaryen (son of Jaehaerys I)\">Aemon Targaryen (son of Jaehaerys I)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Aemon_Targaryen_(son_of_Viserys_II)\" title=\"Aemon Targaryen (son of Viserys II)\">Aemon Targaryen (son of Viserys II)</a>, called the <i>Dragonknight</i></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Aemon_Targaryen_(son_of_Maekar_I)\" title=\"Aemon Targaryen (son of Maekar I)\">Aemon Targaryen (son of Maekar I)</a>, better known as Maester Aemon</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Aemon_Targaryen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: See also\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Aemond_Targaryen\" title=\"Aemond Targaryen\">Aemond Targaryen</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Daemon_Targaryen\" title=\"Daemon Targaryen\">Daemon Targaryen</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Aemon_(disambiguation)\" title=\"Aemon (disambiguation)\">Aemon (disambiguation)</a></li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403153227\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.003 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.004 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 3/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,